      "span_text": "Some studies successfully harness social aspects of image labelling, such as the ESP Game [CITATION_1] , where users compete to label as many images as possible in a set amount of time, but for specialised databases with sensitive applications in medicine or security, this approach is impractical and manual annotation is beyond reach.",
